IMO these settings are a bit too aggressive for issues. I did a PR in https://github.com/apache/incubator-druid/pull/7936 that I am hoping is more appropriate to issues. Also, it fixes the wording config (this patch doesn't set the comment text properly for issues, since the text is under the `pulls` section).
I raised a thread on dev@druid too just to see if anyone else has some thoughts.
